74622::$$$message_0683_0000_0000$$$::"...Phew."[lr]::
74623::$$$message_0683_0000_0001$$$::I set down my empty bowl with a [font italic=true]clink[font italic=false].[lr]::
74624::$$$message_0683_0000_0002$$$::But all of the side dishes on the table are still untouched.[lr]::
74625::$$$message_0683_0000_0003$$$::It took all my effort just to focus on my soup and rice, so I didn't even notice the other food.::
74626::$$$message_0683_0001_0000$$$::Sorry, Sakura. But I'm at my wits' end.[lr]::
74627::$$$message_0683_0001_0001$$$::I need some time away in my room to cool my head.::
74628::$$$message_0683_0002_0000$$$::"...Um, Senpai? Is breakfast not to your liking?"[lr]::
74629::$$$message_0683_0002_0001$$$::"...Oof."[lr]::
74630::$$$message_0683_0002_0002$$$::The tactical retreat ends in failure.[lr]::
74631::$$$message_0683_0002_0003$$$::My escape route was cut off before I knew it.::
74632::$$$message_0683_0003_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
74633::$$$message_0683_0003_0001$$$::I silently hold out my rice bowl.::
74634::$$$message_0683_0004_0000$$$::"Oh, you want seconds! I made a lot, so be sure to eat it all!"[lr]::
74635::$$$message_0683_0004_0001$$$::Sakura returns my bowl with an extra-large helping of rice, and breakfast resumes.::
74636::$$$message_0683_0005_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
74637::$$$message_0683_0005_0001$$$::...Oh, well. I'll just have to deal with this.[lr]::
74638::$$$message_0683_0005_0002$$$::I'm already the only one blushing, so I can't let every single thing Sakura does throw me for a loop.::
74639::$$$message_0683_0006_0000$$$::Still, though...[lr]::
74640::$$$message_0683_0006_0001$$$::"Wait, Sakura. Don't we have a problem here?"::
74641::$$$message_0683_0007_0000$$$::"Hm? What problem, Senpai?"[lr]::
74642::$$$message_0683_0007_0001$$$::She looks at me in puzzlement.[lr]::
74643::$$$message_0683_0007_0002$$$::In other words,[lr]::
74644::$$$message_0683_0007_0003$$$::Sakura doesn't see a problem with Rider sitting silently next to us.::
74645::$$$message_0683_0008_0000$$$::"I mean..."[lr]::
74646::$$$message_0683_0008_0001$$$::I glance at Rider.[lr]::
74647::$$$message_0683_0008_0002$$$::She seems to notice the imbalance I'm getting at.[lr]::
74648::$$$message_0683_0008_0003$$$::"There's no need to concern yourself with me. Continue your meal."[lr]::
74649::$$$message_0683_0008_0004$$$::She urges, just as gracefully as Sakura.::
74650::$$$message_0683_0009_0000$$$::"Huh? Are you worried about her?"[lr]::
74651::$$$message_0683_0009_0001$$$::"It appears so. It's true we have come into conflict several times.[lr]::
74652::$$$message_0683_0009_0002$$$::He must be uncomfortable sharing a table with an enemy."::
74653::$$$message_0683_0010_0000$$$::"That's not true. Senpai doesn't hold it against you, Rider."[lr]::
74654::$$$message_0683_0010_0001$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
74655::$$$message_0683_0010_0002$$$::...Well, this is a pickle.[lr]::
74656::$$$message_0683_0010_0003$$$::I don't resent Rider, but she's on the A-list of people I'm bad at dealing with.::
74657::$$$message_0683_0011_0000$$$::"...Perhaps.[lr]::
74658::$$$message_0683_0011_0001$$$::It seems he's having trouble eating because I am here. I can take my leave if I am being a nuisance."[lr]::
74659::$$$message_0683_0011_0002$$$::"I'm telling you, it isn't like that. You don't mind if Rider joins us, do you, Senpai?"::
74660::$$$message_0683_0012_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
74661::$$$message_0683_0012_0001$$$::I'm in a tough spot.[lr]::
74662::$$$message_0683_0012_0002$$$::But, I'll say...[lr]::Ì